OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain and brisk winds will move
OL,6,Fnortheast through the morning. Drier
OL,7,Fwith perhaps some brightness across
OL,8,Fsome southern and central areas during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling milder for all.
OL,10,FTurning windy in the west later as
OL,11,Ffurther rain arrives by evening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWindy in the west with
OL,14,Fcoastal gales. Rain in the west slowly
OL,15,Fedging eastwards and easing, turning
OL,16,Fdry across Northern Ireland by
OL,17,Fmorning. A mild night for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
